---
title: David Burtka’s Herb-Roasted Chicken Legs with Brown Butter Veggies & Rice
description: Professional chef David and Neil Patrick Harris are a dynamic duo, proving that some things are just better together. Same goes for this recipe: Chicken legs, featuring both a drumstick and a thigh, make the ultimate 2-in-1 combo with juicy dark meat and crispy-crackly skin! David seasons his chicken with earthy Herbes de Provence, roasts it until tender, and serves it over jasmine rice with brown butter asparagus and carrots for a flavorful match that was simply meant to be.
